1 DAY LEFT TO ENTER!

3️⃣ Use #coupleupwithboohoo

🏆Here’s everything you could win:
✨Your own photoshoot
✨Your own boohoo edit
✨A launch event to celebrate your edit
✨Your name added to the boohoo VIP event list for 1 year
✨Your own billboard!

You’ve got until midnight on Friday 3rd September to enter. GOOD LUCK!

T&C's apply: https://bit.ly/3iSJPnS
